divs: sighting detailsi see a red brick house at edge of the field with my eyes but when i take a picture the house looks like a silver\gun metal grey disk on the ground. the area in the foreground is hazy and distorted yet all in my immediate foreground is focused and clear? any theories?
Summary: I take pictures of the field for UFOs, with my eyes I see a house but through the camera I see a UFO on the ground along with small craft.
